data.description: ATTN ALL VETERANS & ACTIVE DUTY ! Huge price reduction of 50k PLUS a 100% Assumable 30 year Fixed Rate Loan at 2.25%....Welcome to your dream home in beautiful Panama City, Florida! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this property boasts numerous upgrades and amenities that make it a must-see.Step into a spacious, light-filled living space with modern upgrades throughout. The open concept design creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining.Enjoy peace of mind with a brand-new metal roof installed in 2019. It not only adds durability but also enhances the home's curb appeal.Escape the Florida heat in your very own private oasis! The inground pool is perfect for cooling off, relaxing, and hosting poolside BBQs.The backyard is fully enclosed with a privacy fence, providing you with a tranquil retreat where you can unwind without disturbance. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or watching the sunset on the spacious covered front porch that extends the entire length of the home. It's the ideal spot to enjoy the outdoors, rain or shine.This home is just minutes away from the local military base, making it an excellent choice for military personnel looking for a convenient and comfortable place to call home.You'll have quick access to shopping, dining, schools, and parks, making it easy to enjoy all that Panama City has to offer.Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a beautifully upgraded home with a private pool in Panama City, FL. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this your new home sweet home!
